<P1para>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/1/1/made/welsh" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/1/1" id="regulation-1-1">
<Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>Enw’r Rheoliadau hyn yw Rheoliadau Addysg (Diwygiadau sy’n Ymwneud â Chydlynu Trefniadau Derbyn Ysgolion) (Cymru) 2024.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/1/2/made/welsh" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/1/2" id="regulation-1-2">
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>Daw’r Rheoliadau hyn i rym ar 4 Tachwedd 2024.</Text>
</P2para>
