<Title>Diwygio Rheoliadau Addysg (Cydlynu Trefniadau Derbyn Ysgolion a Diwygiadau Amrywiol) (Cymru) 2024</Title>
<P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/2/made/welsh" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/2" id="regulation-2">
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P1para>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/2/1/made/welsh" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/2/1" id="regulation-2-1">
<Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>Mae Rheoliadau Addysg (Cydlynu Trefniadau Derbyn Ysgolion a Diwygiadau Amrywiol) (Cymru) 2024<FootnoteRef Ref="f00003"/> wedi eu diwygio fel a ganlyn.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/2/2/made/welsh" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/2/2" id="regulation-2-2">
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>Yn rheoliad 2(1)—</Text>
<P3 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/2/2/a/made/welsh" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/2/2/a" id="regulation-2-2-a">
<Pnumber>a</Pnumber>
<P3para>
<Text>yn y diffiniad o “cynllun Gweinidogion Cymru”, yn lle “is-adran” rhodder “adran”, a</Text>
</P3para>
</P3>
<P3 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/2/2/b/made/welsh" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/2/2/b" id="regulation-2-2-b">
<Pnumber>b</Pnumber>
<P3para>
<Text>hepgorer y diffiniad o “diwrnod gwaith”.</Text>
</P3para>
</P3>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/2/3/made/welsh" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/2/3" id="regulation-2-3">
<Pnumber>3</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>Yn rheoliad 7(3)(a), yn lle “578(1)” rhodder “578”.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
</P1para>
</P1>
</P1group>
<P1group>
<Title>Diwygio Rheoliadau Gwybodaeth Ysgolion (Cymru) 2011</Title>
<P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/3/made/welsh" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/wsi/2024/1002/regulation/3" id="regulation-3">
<Pnumber>3</Pnumber>
<P1para>
<Text>Yn Rheoliadau Gwybodaeth Ysgolion (Cymru) 2011<FootnoteRef Ref="f00004"/>, yn lle is-baragraff (2) o baragraff 5A o Atodlen 2 rhodder—</Text>
<BlockAmendment Context="unknown" Format="double" TargetClass="unknown" TargetSubClass="unknown">
<P2>
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>Yn y paragraff hwn—</Text>
<UnorderedList Class="Definition" Decoration="none">
<ListItem>
<Para>
<Text>mae i “<Term>cais</Term>” (“<Term><Emphasis>application</Emphasis></Term>”) yr ystyr a roddir yn rheoliad 2(1) o Reoliadau 2024;</Text>
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>
<Text>mae i “<Term>cylch derbyn arferol</Term>” (“<Term><Emphasis>normal admission round</Emphasis></Term>”) yr ystyr a roddir yn rheoliad 2(2) o Reoliadau 2024;</Text>
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>
<Text>ystyr “<Term>y cynllun ar gyfer cydlynu trefniadau derbyn yr awdurdod lleol</Term>” (“<Term><Emphasis>the scheme for co-ordinating admission arrangements of the local authority</Emphasis></Term>”) yw—</Text>
<OrderedList Type="alpha" Decoration="parens">
<ListItem>
<Para>
<Text>cynllun a fabwysiedir gan awdurdod lleol yn unol â rheoliad 4(1) o Reoliadau 2024, neu</Text>
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>
<Text>cynllun a osodir ar yr awdurdod lleol gan Weinidogion Cymru yn unol ag adran 89B(2) o Ddeddf 1998;</Text>
</Para>
</ListItem>
</OrderedList>
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>
<Text>mae i “<Term>ffurflen gais gyffredin</Term>” (“<Term><Emphasis>common application form</Emphasis></Term>”) yr ystyr a roddir yn rheoliad 2(1) o Reoliadau 2024.</Text>
</Para>
</ListItem>
</UnorderedList>
</P2para>
</P2>
</BlockAmendment>
</P1para>
</P1>
</P1group>
